    "body": "### When using Enter-PSSession\r\n**Results**\r\n```powershell\r\n[administrator@[0::0]]: PS > get-acl\r\nCommand 'get-acl' was not run as the session in which it was intended to run was either closed or broken\r\nPS />\r\n```\r\n----\r\n**Expected**\r\n```powershell\r\n[administrator@[0::0]]: PS > get-acl\r\nConnection disconnected,Trying to reconnect\r\nDirectory: C:\\Users\\Administrator\r\nPath      Owner                  Access\r\n----      -----                  ------\r\nDocuments BUILTIN\\Administrators NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM Allow  Fu…\r\n[administrator@[0::0]]: PS >\r\n```\r\nor\r\n```powershell\r\n[administrator@[0::0]]: PS > get-acl\r\nConnection disconnected,Whether to reconnect[y/n]? y\r\nDirectory: C:\\Users\\Administrator\r\nPath      Owner                  Access\r\n----      -----                  ------ \r\nDocuments BUILTIN\\Administrators NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM Allow  Fu…\r\n[administrator@[0::0]]: PS >\r\n```",
